  Ji5-chhiaN2, goa2 ma7 e7-tang3 ka7 koh khah cheng-chhai2 chim3 ti7 loan5-ai3 tiong kiat-hap8 e5 iah8-a2 e5 cheng5-heng5 lai5 kong2 hou7 lin2 thiaN. Che si7 hoat-seng ti7 goa2 chhou-tiong ji7-ni5 tu2-a2 beh kiat-sok hit tang, ia7 tioh8 si7 goa2 chap8-gou7-hoe3 hit-chun7 e5 cha2-chhun. U7 chit8-kang, goa2 ti7 im-gak8-sek leh toaN5 piano, ui3 phah-khui e5 thang-a2-mng5 poe-jip8 lai5 u7 chin sui2 e5 sit e5 iah8-a2, m7-chai si7 an2-choaN2, iah8-a2 choaN5 poe loh8-lai5 theng5 ti7 li7 goa2 e5 chhiu2 bo5 loa7 hng7 e5 keyboard teng2-koan5. Tu2-a2 ho2 siuN7 beh iong7 chhiu2 ka7 I sng2 chit8-leh e5 si5-chun7, goa2 chiah hoat-hian7 I peng7 m7-si7 kan-taN chit8-chiah nia7-nia7, sou2-i2 goa2 choaN5 chhiu2 tong3 tiau5 bo5 khi3 ka7 bong. Tong-jian5, in nng7-chiah na2-chhin-chhiuN7 khi3 hou7 teng-a2 teng3 tiau5 leh kang7-khoan2, liam5 kah an5-an5-an5. Ji5-chhiaN2, ma7 chhin-chhiuN7 lang5 lim-chiu2-chui3 kang7-khoan2, haiN3 lai5 haiN3 khi3. Tioh8 ti7 chit-e5 si5-chun7, goa2 e5 sim-koaN lai7 goan5-pun2 lian5-bin2 e5 sim soah khi3 hou7 chan5-jim2 e5 sim lai5 chhu2-tai7. ThiaN hou7 chheng-chho2, ki5-sit8 goa2 chit-e5 lang5 ui3 siau3-lian5 si5-tai7 khai-si2 kau3 chheng-lian5 si5-tai7 e7-tang3 kong2 bo5 saN2 tong5-cheng5-sim. Pok8-lek8 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 tioh8 si7 goa2 e5 hoa3-sin kang7-khoan2, e7-tang3 pho3-hoai7 e5 goa2 choat8-tui3 siuN7 pan7-hoat ka7 I pho3-hoai7. Che si7 in-ui7 ti7 goa2 e5 sim-koaN lai7 san2-seng liau2 chit8-chiong2 hoan2-phoan3 e5 i3-sek, chit-e5 i3-sek lai5 cho2-iu7 tioh8 goa2 e5 heng5-ui5. Goa2 siuN7 chit-ma2 goa2 ia7 siong-sin3 che3-iok kui-e5 u2-tiu7 e5 toa7 to7-li2---mau5-tun2-lut8, choat8-tui3 bo5 kho2-leng5 ka7 goa2 pai5-tu5 ti7 goa7-khau2. Sou2-i2 pun2-te2 goa2 e5 seng3-cheng5 si7 khah loan2-jiok8 e5, kiat-ko2 goa2 sou2 piau2-hian7 chhut-lai5 e5 heng5-ui5 tian-to3 long2 si7 chan5-jim2 koh tang3-sng. Goa2 cho3 chit8-kiaN7 chin bo5 eng3-kai cho3 e5 tai7-chi3 ah. Goa2 ka7 hit nng7-chiah boe7 ki3-tit thang poe, hong3-khi3 seN3-mia7 e5 iah8-a2 liah8 khi2-lai5, soah loh8-khi3, li2 siuN7 goa2 an2-choaN2 piN3? Ka2-su2 kong2 lui5-kong phah kau3 thau5-khak teng2-koan5 ma7 bo5 kho2-leng5 e7 hun-khui hit nng7-chiah iah8-a2, goa2 nge7-si2 siuN7 beh iong7 chhiu2 ka7 in lai5 thiah hun-khui. Pun2-te2 goa2 kio7-si7 kong2 che si7 chit8-kiaN7 kan2-tan e5 khang-khoe3, tan7-si7 siuN7 be7 kau3 khah an2-choaN2 ka7 in giu2 long2 bo5 hoat-tou7 ka7 in thiah hun-khui. Sou2-i2 goa2 chi2-ho2 un7-khi3 iong7 koh-khah-che7 e5 lat8 lai5 ka7 in giu2, siong7 boe2-a2 in chiah hou7 goa2 lai5 ka7 thiah hun-khui. Koh lai5, goa2 ka7 in khng3 ti7 piano e5 keyboard teng2-koan5, goa2 siuN7 kong2 in chha-put-to si7 e7 poe-chau2 chiah tioh8. Tan7-si7, su7-sit8 kah goa2 siuN7 e5 oan5-choan5 to3-peng2, in put-tan7 bo5 poe-chau2, tian-to3 koh chai3 iong7 in bo5 saN2 su3-phoe3 sio2-sio2 e5 seng-khu kah toa7-toa7 e5 sit-a2, io5-io5-haiN3-haiN3 e5 hou7-siong koh tau3-tin7. Li2 kam2-kak kong2 goa2 khoaN3 tioh8 chit-khoan2 e5 cheng5-heng5 kho2-leng5 e7 chhai2-chhu2 saN2-mih8 khoan2 e5 chhiu2-toaN7 lai5 tui3-thai7 in leh? Ka7 in phah hou7 si2? Goa2 chiah bo5 hiah gong7 leh. Goa2 ia7-m7 si7 kong2 m7-chai beh an2-choaN2 chin-chiaN3 lai5 khou2-tok8 lang5, khou2-tok8 lang5 m7-si7 ka7 phoaN3 si2-heng5, si7 tauh8-tauh8-a2 iong7 kok-chiong2 e5 hong-hoat lai5 ka7 I heng5-kiu5, kam2 m7-si7 leh. Sou2-i2, goa2 ka7 hit nng7-chiah iah8-a2 liah8 khi2-lai5, chit8-chiah liah8 ti7 chiaN3-chhiu2, chit8-chiah liah8 ti7 to3-chhiu2, jian5-au7, ka7 in nng7-chiah hiong3 nng7-e5 oan5-choan5 to3-peng2 e5 hong-hiong3 koan5-koan5 tan3 khi3. Goa2 chan5-jim2 ji5-chhiaN2 ai3 kang5 chhong3-khang e5 sim-thai7 toh8 ti7 chia hoat-hui kau3 siong7 koan5 e5 keng3-kai3. Goa2 chit-e5 lang5 chin-chiaN3 si7 u7 ka3 ou-peh8 loan7 lai5, chi2-iau3 si7 bo5 chiau3-li2-chhut-pai5 e5 tai7-chi3, goa2 long2 u7 kho2-leng5 cho3 e7 chhut-lai5. Sou2-i2 li2 ai3 tek8-piat chu3-i3 goa2 chit-tiam2. Siong7-be2 hit nng7-chiah iah8-a2 u7 koh poe tau3-tin7 bo5 si7 m7? Tong-jian5 in si7 thau5-hin5-bak8-am3, ia7 si7 chui3-bong5-bong5 kang7-khoan2, i2 hiong3 koan5 tan3 chhut-khi3 e5 hit-e5 khong-kan ui5 tiong-sim, it-tit8 ti7 hit lai7-te2 seh8 khou-a2, hou7-siong piaN3-mia7 leh chau2-chhoe7 sit-soaN3 e5 leng7-goa7 chit8-poaN3. Tan7-si7, un7-mia7 soah ka7 in khan-in2 lu2-lai5-lu2-hng7 e5 nng7-e5 kek-toan e5 hong-hiong3. Jian5-au7, in na2-chhin-chhiuN7 ti7 kang7 chit8-e5 si5-chun7 ui3 chiu2-chui3 tiong chheng-chheN2 khi2-lai5 kang7-khoan2, hiong5-hiong5 hiong3 to3-peng2 e5 hong-hiong3 hng7-hng7 e5 poe-khi3. Goa2 siuN7 ti7 chit-e5 khong3-khoah e5 se3-kai3 tiong, in chit-si3-lang5 long2 bo5 kho2-leng5 u7 koh chai3 saN kiN3-bin7 e5 ki-hoe7 ah.
  Goa2 kho2-leng5 kong2 siuN-che7 iah8-a2 e5 kou3-su7 ah. Goa2 goan5-pun2 siuN7 beh sio2-khoa2 lai5 kong2 koh khah jiat8 e5 ti e5 tai7-chi3, koh khah beng2 e5 gu5 e5 kou3-su7, iah-si7 koh khah sim-sek e5 choa5 e5 cheng5-heng5 lai5 hou7 li2 thiaN. Tan7-si7, chit-ma2 iah-si7 mai3 kong2 ho2 ah. Na7-si7 li2 ai3 thiaN, goa2 siong-sin3 goa2 u7 hoat-tou7 chiu7 kok-chiong2 bo5 kang7 e5 seng-but8 chit8-hang7 chit8-hang7 a2 lai5 kong2 hou7 li2 liau2-kai2. Phi3-ju5 kong2 niu5-a2,...goa2 siuN7 ia7 si7 ti7 chia tong3 khi2-lai5 ho2 ah, goa2 chin-chiaN3 si7 oe7-hou2-lan7 oe7 siuN koe3-thau5 a2. Ka2-su2 kong2, goa2 na7-si7 ka7 goa2 bou2 chit8-kang, iah-si7 bou2 chit8-hun-cheng sou2 khoaN3 tioh8, sou2 thiaN tioh8, ah si7 sou2 siuN7 tioh8 e5 toa7-sio2 hang7 tai7-chi3, chit8-tiau5 chit8-tiau5 lai5 kong2 loh8-khi3, khiong2-kiaN e7 ai3 khai saN-ko3-goeh8 e5 si5-kan chiah kong2 e7 liau2. Goa2 si7 bo5 hiah che7 e5 si5-kan. Goa2 siong-sin3 li2 ma7 si7 bo5 hiah eng5 chiah tioh8. Sou2-i2, ui7 tioh8 beh ka7 goa2 e5 ai3-cheng5 kou3-su7 iong7 khah kan2-tan, khah tiong7-tiam2-sek e5 hong-hoat lai5 kong2, goa2 si7 siuN7 kah kiong5-beh khi2-siau2 ah. 
  Goa2 ka7 bo5 siaN2 tiong7-iau3 e5 tai7-chi3 kong2 siuN-che7 ah. Ki5-sit8, goa2 siuN7 beh kong2 hou7 li2 thiaN e5 si7 tui3 chit-ma2 khai-si2. Ti7 beh cheng3-sek khai-kang2 chin3-cheng5, bo5-lun7 ju5-ho5, goa2 su-iau3 koh chai3 kong2 chit8-kiaN7 se3-hang7 e5 tai7-chi3. 
  Ji7 
  Ti7 chit8-khai-si2 goa2 i2-keng kong2-koe3, goa2 kan-taN siuN7 beh loan5-ai3. Ji5-chhiaN2, it-sim-it-i3 cho3 loan5-ai3 e5 bang7. Loan5-ai3 na2-chhin-chhiuN7 si7 goa2 ui5-it e5 ng3-bang7. ChhiuN7 goa2 chit-khoan2 e5 chhit-tho5-a2 pun2-te2 tioh8 bo5 kho2-leng5 u7 saN2-mih8 li2-siong2, iah-si7 hi-bang7. Tui3 it-poaN lang5 lai5 kong, in sou2 tui-kiu5 e5 ho2 mia5-siaN, seng5-chiu7, iah-si7 chai5-hu3......teng2-teng2, goa2 si7 koh khah bo5 kho2-leng5 khi3 kho2-lu7 koe3. Tiam3 goa2 e5 sim-koaN lai7 kan-taN siuN7 beh an5-an5 ka7 goa2 sou2 jit8-su-ia7-bang7 e5 hit-e5 cha-bou2 gin2-a2 pho7 ti7 goa2 e5 heng-kham2 lai7-te2. Si7, he si7 goa2 chin-chiaN3 ui5-it e5 siuN7-hoat. Chit-ma2 goa2 ma7 si7 an2-ne siuN7. Ah, goa2 sou2 sim-ai3 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-a2, goa2 siuN7 beh iong7 goa2 e5 chhiu2 an5-an5 lai5 ka7 li2 lam2 tiau5 leh, chiong li2 na2-chhin-chhiuN7 thng5-bit8 e5 chhui3-tun5 kam5 leh, jian5-au7, ti7 goa2 e5 seng-khu kah li2 e5 seng-khu hap8 cho3 chit8-e5 e5 si5-chun7, " goa2 " chit-e5 khai3-liam7 chiah thau5 chit8-kai2 e7-tang3 oan5-choan5 the2-thian7 chhut-lai5. Chit-khoan2 e5 siuN7-hoat na7 ti7 goa2 e5 sim-koaN lai7 puh-ge5, I tioh8 e7 chin kin2 e5 sok-tou7 lai5 seng5-tiong2, bo5-loa7-ku2 liau2-au7, I tioh8 e7 ti7 goa2 e5 seng-khu lai7 teng3-kin. Li2 kam2 e7-tang3 siong-sin3, ti7 chit8-e5 se3-kan siong7, u7 goa2 chit-khoan2 siau2 ti-ko leh? M7-koh, goa2 chu7-se3-han3 tioh8 it-tit8 ng3-bang7 ka-ki7 e7-tang3 cho3 chit8-e5 siau2-lang5, tong-jian5 che si7 bo5 saN2-mih8 thang ho2 chhau3-toaN7, tan7-si7 goa2 iah-si7 kam2-kak tui3 ka-ki7 chin boan2-chiok. Si7 an2-choaN2 goa2 e7 pian3-cho3 chit-khoan2 e5 lang5, goa2 siuN7 chiaN5 khiau2 e5 li2 eng3-kai bo5 su-iau3 goa2 koh ke bo5-chhai2 chhui3-chih8, chu7-thau5-kau3-boe2 koh soat-beng5 chit8-kai2 hou7 li2 thiaN, ui3 thau5-tu2-a2 goa2 kong2 goa2 siau3-lian5 si5-tai7 e5 kou3-su7 lai7-te2, goa2 siuN7 li2 chha-put-to u7 chit8-e5 te2 chiah tioh8. Li2 kong2 goa2 chiok bo5-liau5 si7 m7? Tan7-si7, goa2 kam2-kak lan2 lang5 e5 su-siong2 iah-si7 kam2-cheng5 e5 hoat-seng kah chin3-tian2, ki5-sit8 long2 si7 ui3 bo5-liau5, iu3-ti7, iah-si7 se3-hang7 tai7-chi3 khai-si2 e5. Ji5-chhiaN2, tui3 mui2 chit8-e5 lang5 lai5 kong2, chi-phoe3 in chit8-si3-lang5 chin-chiaN3 tiong7-iau3 e5 se3-hang7 tai7-chi3 iu7-koh sui5 lang5 bo5-kang7 u7 chin toa7 e5 chha-piat8. Na7 chiau3 an2-ne kong2 khi2-lai5, goa2 ui3 goa2 e5 se3-kai3 tiong lai5 the5-chhut chit8-tho3 kah tioh8 goa2 e5 hoeh kah goa2 e5 bah e5 su-kho2 the2-he7, ma7 m7-si7 bo5 kho2-leng5 e5, kam2 m7-si7 leh? 
  Goa2 chin-chiaN3 chiok ng3-bang7 u7 chit8-e5 ai3-jin5. Sou2-i2, goa2 e5 sim-cheng5 chin thong3-khou2, goa2 e5 khi2-mou si7 siau2-siau2 bo5 siaN2 cheng3-siong5. Mui2 chit8-am3, goa2 beh khun3 chin3-cheng5, goa2 long2 e7 liam7 kong2: " Ai3-jin5 ah, ho2 khun3 loh8. " chiah khun3. Tong-jian5 in-ui7 bo5 chit-e5 lang5, sou2-i2 goa2 bo5 hoat-tou7 kio3 chhut I e5 mia5 lai5, che si7 sio2-khoa2 bo5 chhai2 e5 sou2-chai7. Ji5-chhiaN2, u7 si5 ti7 poaN3-me5 chheN2 khi2-lai5 e5 si5-chun7, ti7 goa2 e5 sim-koaN lai7-te2 it-teng7 u7 ai3-jin5 e5 heng5-iaN2 chau2 chhut-lai5. Sui-jian5, goa2 m7-bat I, tan7-si7, I it-teng7 long2 e7 po2-chhi5 I seng3-lu2 poaN e5 chhio3-iong5 khia7 ti7 goa2 e5 bin7-thau5-cheng5. Ti7 chit-e5 si5-chun7, goa2 it-teng7 long2 e7 iong7 chin khian5-seng5 e5 sim-cheng5 lai5 ka7 bak8-chiu kheh khi2-lai5, in-ui7 goa2 kam2-kak kong2, ai3-jin5 e5 chu-iong5 sit8-chai7 si7 chiok seng5 koan-im-phou5-sat, ti7 I e5 seng-khu piN, goa2 tiaN7-tiaN7 e7-tang3 khoaN3 tioh8 na2-chhin-chhiuN7 sin5-beng5 kang7-khoan2 e5 kng-khoan5. Jian5-au7, goa2 e7 ka7 goa2 e5 siang-chhiu2 chhng chhut-lai5, an5-an5 e5 chiong I lam2 leh, toa7-siaN hoah chhut, ah! Goa2 sou2 ai3 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-a2! Ti7 chit-e5 se3-kai3 tiong goa2 siong7 kah-i3 e5 lang5! Goa2 siuN7 beh iong7 goa2 chhiong-boan2 jiat8-cheng5 e5 chhui3-tun5 khi3 chim li2, iong7 goa2 moa2-pak e5 ai3-i3 lai5 ka7 goa2 e5 ai3-jin5 lam2 tiau5 leh, goa2 e5 heng-kham2 ma7 in-ui7 jiat8-cheng5 koe3-tou7, kiong5-beh hoe2-sio khi2-lai5. Tui3 I su-bou7 e5 sim-cheng5 chham bak8-sai2 ma7 kiong5-beh lau5 chhut-lai5 ah.
  Chin sit-le2, bo5-tiuN-bo5-ti5 tiong goa2 soah sit-thai7 ah. Tan7-si7, goa2 e5 heng-kham2 kau3 chit-ma2 ma7 na2-chhin-chhiuN7 kiong5-beh pit khui kang7-khoan2. Li2 ma7 chai-iaN2 goa2 e5 kha-kin kah chhiu2-kin ma7 chhin-chhiuN7 kiu3-kin kang7-khoan2, it-tit8 chhoah boe7 theng5. In-ui7 si7 li2, goa2 chiah e7 bin7-phoe5 hiah kau7, kong2 hiah-nih-a2 che7. Na7-si7 oaN7 cho3 pat8-lang5, goa2 choat8-tui3 bo5 kho2-leng5 u7 sim-cheng5 kong2 chit-khoan2 oe7 lai5. In-ui7 ti7 li2 e5 bin7-thau5-cheng5, goa2 be7 chiok koa3-i3 goa2 ka-ki7 e5 heng5-siong7. ChhiaN2 li2 liau2-kai2, it-tit8 kau3 taN, goa2 m7-bat kong2 ka7 chin-chiaN3 e5 ka-ki7 oan5-oan5-choan5-choan5 piau2-hian7 chhut-lai5. Tan7-si7 li2, sian7-liong5 koh tan-sun5 e5 li2, chhiaN2 li2 bo5-lun7 ju5-ho5 it-teng7 ai3 liau2-kai2 goa2. Goa2 si7 cheng-seN. Na7 kong2 seng3-hian5 e5 lou7 si7 lan2 lang5 eng3-kai kiaN5 e5 lou7, goa2 hun-beng5 si7 kiaN5 m7 tioh8 lou7 ah. Sou2-i2, chhiaN2 li2 ka7 goa2 khoaN3 bo5-khi2. Tan7-si7 chhiaN2 li2 m7-thang lai5 chhio3 goa2, chong2-si7 cheng-seN si7 e7-sai2 lai5 ka7 I khoaN3 bo5-khi2, tan7-si7 ma7 be7-sai2 lai5 ka7 thi2-chhio3. Koh chai3 kong2 che ma7 m7-si7 saN2-mih8 ho2 thang thi2-chhio3 e5 tai7-chi3. Iu2 koan chit-tiam2, goa2 teh siuN7, ka2-su2 lan2 chit-e5 te7-kiu5 na7 koh chit8-kai2 hoe5-hok tioh8 chhiong-boan2 cheng-seN e5 si5-tai7 toh8 ho2 loh8. ChhiaN2 li2 m7-thang siu7-khi3, goa2 peng7 m7-si7 hi-bang7 jin5-lui7 lai5 choat8-cheng2. Goa2 e5 i3-su3 si7 kong2, goa2 hi-bang7 lan2 e7-sai2 lai5 ka7 lan2 chit-ma2 sou2 koan3-si3 e5 seng-oah8 hong-sek kah bun5-hoa3 sou3-iong2 lai5 ka7 pang3-sat, it-chhe3 hoe5-hok kau3 siong7 kou2-cha2 e5 ia2-ban5 chong7-thai7 lai5 koh khai-si2. Goa2 lai5 ku2 chit8-e5 sit8-che3 e5 le7, phi3-ju5 kong2, u7 e5 lang5 m7-si7 ui7 tioh8 beh po2-loan2 lai5 ha5 phoaN7-kin, in si7 ui7 tioh8 beh tian2 in khai kui2-pah-khou be2 e5 mih8-kiaN7, sou2-i2 chiah ka7 ha5 ti7 keng-kah-thau5. Tui3 chit-khoan2 e5 tai7-chi3, goa2 si7 chiok chi3-chan3 be7 tiau5. Chi2-iau3 li2 chu3-