   Chin sit-le2, oe7 iu7-koh kong2 hng7 khi3 ah. Na2-chhin-chhiuN7 pian3 kah chiaN5 leng2 e5 khoan2. Goa7-khau2 bo5 tek-khak i2-keng khai-si2 leh loh8-seh ah. Kong2 khi2 lai5, kin ni5 ma7 chin ki5-koai3, kau3 taN iah m7-bat loh8 koe3 chit8 kai2 seh, bin5-a2-chai3 tioh8 i2-keng si7 ki-tok Ia5-sou e5 seN-jit8 ah. Kong2 tioh8 chit kang, goa2 toh8 khi3 siuN7 tioh8 goa2 ma7 si7 ti7 hit kang e5 poaN3-mi5 si5 chhut-si3 e5. Sou2-i2, bin5-a2-chai3 tioh8 si7 goa2 e5 seN-jit8 lah. Li2 mng7 goa2 kui2 hoe3 si7 m7? Li2 mng7 tioh8 chit8 kiaN7 hou7 goa2 chin pi-siong e5 tai7-chi3 ah. Kau3 bin5-a2-chai3 e5 poaN3-mi5, goa2 tioh8 saN-chap8 hoe3 ah. Au7 jit8 e5 cha2-khi2, tng goa2 ka7 goa2 e5 bak8-chiu peh khui khai-si2, goa2 tioh8 it-teng7 ai3 ka7 ka-ki7 sng3 cho3 saN-chap8-it hoe3 e5 lang5 chiah e7-sai2. Sou2-i2, kin-a2-jit si7 goa2 saN-chap8 hoe3 e5 siong7 boe2-a2 chit8-kang. Lau2-sit8 kong2, goa2 si7 oan5-choan5 boe7 ki3-tit chit kiaN7 tai7-chi3 ah. Chit-ma2 ti7 bo5-tiuN-ti5 tang-tiong khi3 siuN7-tioh8 chit-e5 i3-goa7 e5 siau-sit, goa2 si7 chit8 poaN3 hoaN-hi2 ma7 chit8 poaN3 siong-sim. SiuN7 tioh8 saN-chap8 hoe3, goa2 e5 chheng-chhun toh8 i2-keng pian3-cho3 koe3-khi3, siau-sit ah. Li2 chap8-poeh hoe3 si7 m7 ? Si7 an2-choaN2 li2 beh ka7 chit kiaN7 tai7-chi3 kong2 hou7 goa2 chai-iaN2? Li2 kho2-leng5 m7 chai-iaN2, li2 thau5-tu2-a2 chit ku3 oe7 loa7 chhi3 thiaN3 goa2 e5 sim leh. Tan7-si7, goa2 beh ka7 li2 kong2, li2 hit ku3 oe7 i2-keng oan5-oan5-choan5-choan5 lai5 ka7 goa2 e5 seN3-mia7 kiat-ko2 tan3-sak tiau7. Goa2 e5 chheng-chhun tioh8 ui3 chit-chun7 lai5 kiat-sok ah. Tui3 goa2 lai5 kong2, chheng-chhun put-chai3 e5 seN3-mia7, giam5-keh lai5 kong2, be7-tang3 sng3 si7 seN3-mia7. Chha-put-to goa2 ti7 li2 chit-e5 ni5-hoe3 e5 si5-chun7, goa2 tioh8 u7 chit khoan2 e5 siuN7-hoat ah. Goa2 ti7 goa2 chap8-chhit, peh hoe3 e5 si5-chun7, goa2 toh8 siau3 siuN7 tioh8 loan5-ai3 e5 chu-bi7, siuN7 beh u7 ai3-jin5. Sim7-chi3 ti7 bang7 tiong ma7 si7 leh siuN7 kong2: Goa2 sou2 sim-ai3 e5 lang5 oh, chhiaN2