  Li2, iah siau3-lian5-ke-a2 e5 li2, li2 kam2 chai-iaN2, goa2 e5 cheng-sin5 lai7-pou7 tioh8 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 pun2-te2 si7 phang-kong3-kong3 e5 chiu2 soah khi3 pian3-cho3 hou7 lang5 hiam5 sng e5 chhou3 kang7-khoan2. Goa2 tui3 lang5 goan5-pun2 bo5-han7 e5 ai3, chit-ma2 na2 beh oan5-seng5 hoat-kaN3 chok-iong7, chiong goa2 e5 ai3-i3 choan2-pian3 cho3 kek8-toan e5 oan3-hun7. Sui-jian5, goa2 e5 seN3-mia7 kah chheng-chhun ti7 cheng2-ko3 jin5-lui7 e5 tng5-oan2 lek8-su2 tiong si7 chha-put-to na2 bo5 kang7-khoan2. Tan7-si7, goa2 siong-sin3 goa2 chit-e5 sio2-sio2 e5 oan3-hun7 choat8-tui3 u7 kho2-leng5 e7 tui3 chit-e5 u2-tiu7 san2-seng pho3-hai7 e5 chok-iong7. 
