  Oe7 koh kong2 to3-tng2-lai5, goa2 ma7 bat chhin-sin kam2-kak tioh8 loan5-ai3 e5 chu-bi7 koe3, ma7 bat tu2-koe3 na2-chhin-chhiuN7 si7 goa2 e5 ai3-jin5 e5 lang5. Ka7 siuN7-khi2-lai5, he si7 hoat-seng ti7 goa2 tiong-hak8 si3-ni5, chhiu-thiN beh soah si5-chun7 e5 tai7-chi3. Hak8-hau7 ha7-kho3 liau2, goa2 kah peng5-iu2 khi3 gun2 tiaN7 khi3 e5 hit keng ti7 kong-hng5 hu3-kin7 e5 chit8 keng png7-tiam3 chiah8 thian-put-la2. Gun2 si7 tak8-kang long2 khi3 hia chiah8 thian-put-la2 m7-bat chit kang bo5 khi3. Tak8-kang na7 hak8-hau7 e5 ha7-kho3 si5-kan chit8 kau3, gun2 tioh8 e7 kam2-kak thian-put-la2 e5 bi7 it-tit8 ui3 gun2 e5 phiN7-khang lai5. Hit-chun7 na7 lau7-su iah m7 ha7-kho3 ke3-siok8 leh kong2-kho3, goa2 kah goa2 e5 ho2-peng5-iu2 tioh8 e7 hou7-siong sai2-bak8-boe2, cho3-hoe2 ti7 pak-tou2 lai7 lai5 chhoh-kan3-kiau7. Bo5 loa7 ku2 liau2-au7, chit8 ha7-kho3 kiaN5 koe3 le2, gun2 tioh8 chhiong chhut kau3-sek khi3 ah. Mui2 chit kai2, long2 si7 goa2 chau2 te7-it. Tan7-si7 ma7 chiok che7 kai2 in-ui7 lau7-su iah boe7 hoe5-le2 liau2, iah tioh8 si7 kong2, lau7-su e5 am7-a2-kun2 iah leh oan loh8-khi3 e5 si5-chun7, gun2 tioh8 khai-si2 heng5-tong7 ah. Kiat-ko2 pi7-pek koh teng5 kiaN5-le2 chit kai2. Se3-kan siong7 thai3 u7 chiah bo5-liau5 e5 tai7-chi3 leh. Gun2 chit chau2 chhut kau3-sek tioh8 chong5 ui3 sok-sia3 khi3 ka7 chheh-pau tan3 leh, kha chiok chu7-jian5 tioh8 kiaN5 ui3 thian-put-la2 e5 tiam3 khi3. Goa2 kah peng5-iu2 e5 kha-pou7 chong2 si7 it-ti3 e5. Ui3 hak8-hau7 kau3 thian-put-la2 tiam3, kiaN5 khah kin2, lai5 hoe5 ai3 saN-chap8 hun-cheng. Hak8-hau7 koaiN-mng5 e5 si5-kan si7 gou7-tiam2. Gun2 long2 si7 iok ti7 hak8-hau7 e5 mng5-kha-khau2 tang5-che5 chhut-hoat.
