  Na7-si7 u7 ji7-chap8 hun i2-siong7 e5 si5-chun7, gun2 tioh8 e7 chau2 khi3. Na7 bo5 ji7-chap8 hun cheng e5 si5-chun7, gun2 chi2-ho2 lai5 hong3-khi3. Ti7 hit khoan2 e5 chong7-hong2 chi ha7, gun2 tioh8 chhai2-chhu2 leng7-goa7 e5 hong-hoat. Hak8-hau7 kau2-tiam2 koaiN tian7-hoe2, tan2 tak8-ke khun3 liau2 au7, gun2 nng7-lang5 tioh8 peh chhiuN5 chhut-khi3. Li2 kam2 chai-iaN2, am3-si5 e5 ke-a2-lou7 sit8-chai7 u7-kau3 sui2 ! U7 chit8 kai2, poaN3-mi5 ui3 thian-put-la2 tiam3 tng2-lai5 e5 lou7 tiong, khi3 hou7 kou2-pan2 e5 han3-bun5 lau7-su tu2-tioh8, hit khou keng3-jian5 hiong3 hau7-tiuN2 bit8-ko3, gun2 choaN5 khi3 hong5 chhu2-hoat8 theng5-chi2 lai5 hak8-hau7 siong7-kho3 chit8-le2-pai3, gun2 thiaN-tioh8 chit khoan2 e5 chhu2-hoat8, chiok hoaN-hi2. In-ui7, gun2 tau kah thian-put-la2 tiam3 si7 ti7 kang7 chit8-tiau5 ke, gun2 nng7-lang5 hit le2-pai3 tak8-kang ui3 cha2-khi2 kau3 am3-si5 long2 ma7 si7 ti7 thian-put-la2 tiam3 koe3 e5, se3-kan siong7 sit8-chai7 chiok che7 chit-khoan2 khau-se2 e5 tai7-chi3. In chhu2-hoat8 gun2 e5 pun2-i3 si7 beh chou2-chi2 gun2 koh chau2 khi3 chiah8 thian-put-la2, tan7-si7 kiat-ko2 tian-to3 soah su3 hou7 gun2 khi3 chiah8 thian-put-la2 e5 chu7-iu5. U7 ho2-chhio3 bo5? Bo5 ho2-chhio3 si7 m7? Li2 na7 kam2-kak ho2-chhio3, tioh8 chhiaN2 li2 chu7-iu5 toa7-siaN lai5 chhio3, m7 bian2 kheh-khi3. Li2 thai3 m7 chhio3 leh? Si7 m7 si7 kong2 chiah8 e5 bo5 i3-su3 leh? Na7 an2-ne si7 chiok kho2-sioh e5, in-ui7 na7 kong2 tioh8 chiah8, goa2 u7 chiok che3 kou3-su7 e7-tang3 kong2 hou7 li2 thiaN. 
  Na7 si7 an2-ne, goa2 lai5 kong2 goa2 kah goa2 e5 peng5-iu2 si7 an2-choaN2 khi3 hoat-hian7 tioh8 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 si7 ai3-jin5 e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 e5 kou3-su7. Kou3-su7 si7 an2-ne e5, si7 hoat-seng ti7 le2-pai3, gun2 ui3 cha2-khi2 tioh8 leh seh8-ke. Goa2 e5 peng5-iu2 si7 chit8 e5 tiat-hak8-ka. I siong7 him-siong2 e5 tiat-hak8-ka si7 Schopenhauer, ji5-chhiaN2 jin7-ui5, chit-e5 se3-kai3 chhiong-boan2 tioh8 pi-koan, chhiong-boan2 tioh8 oan3-than3 e5 tai7-chi3. Ti7 hit-chun7, peng5-iu2 kong2 i ka-ki7 ti7 cheng-sin5 siong7 tu2-a2 ho2 si7 khi3 pong7 tioh8 leh toa7 choan2-pian3 e5 si5-chun7. I tui3 goa2 kong2 : ¡§ Si7 an2-choaN2 goa2 e7 hiah gong7 leh, goa2 ui3 kin-a2-jit8 khai-si2 bo5-ai3 koh cho3 tiat-hak8-ka ah. ¡¨ Jian5-au7, i iong7 chit8 e5 tiat-hak8-ka e5 oe7 lai5 soat-beng5 i e5 sim-cheng5. I kong2 :¡§ Tiat-hak8-ka na2 chhin-chhiuN7 si7 ti7 chit8-te3 chin pui5 e5 thou2-te7 siong7 giong7-beh ta khi3 e5 chhau2-a2.¡¨ I koh ke3-siok8 kong2 :¡§Goa2 beh ui3 kin-a2-jit8 khai-si2, hong3-khi3 tiat-hak8, choan-sim lai5 tam5-loan5-ai3.¡¨ Tioh8 an2-ne, goa2 e5 peng5-iu2 siaN-beng5 ui3 chit8 e5 tiat-hak8-ka pian3-cho3 chit8 e5 loan5-ai3-ka khi3 ah. Goa2 si7 bo5 thak8 koe3 loa7 che7 chheh, bo5 hak8-bun7 e5 lang5, sou2-i2 goa2 sui5 tioh8 hoe5-tap i kong2 : ¡§An2-ne siong7 kai3 ho2. ¡¨ lai5 piau2-si7 goa2 tui3 i chit-e5 kai2-pian3 e5 chan3-tong5. Pun2-te2 peng5-iu2 ut-chut e5 sim-cheng5, sui5 choan2-pian3 cho3 hoaN-hi2 e5 chhio3-iong5. I koe3-khi3 si7 koe3 ti7 chin ap-che3 ka-ki7 e5 seng-oah8 tiong, sou2-i2 chit-e5 pian3-hoa3, tui3 goa2 lai5 kong2 si7 chit8 e5 put-chi2-a2 toa7 e5 chhi3-kek. Gun2 tui3 chit-e5 kai2-pian3 kam2-kak chin hoaN-hi2, ji5-chhiaN2 hoaN-hi2 kau3 thiau3 waltze khi2-lai5. Waltze si7 gun2 ui3 ti7 ke-a2-lou7 teng2-koan5 e5 chit8 keng bu2-thiaN thau khoaN3 lai5, kho3 hit kai3 khoaN3 koe3 e5 in3-siong2 oh8 e7-hiau2 e5. Gun2 kiaN5 koe3 khai-si2 u7 loh8 hioh8-a2 e5 phun3-choaN5 kong-hng5, soan2-tek chit8-tiau5 siong7 kai3 lau7-jiat8 e5 lou7 kiaN5 khi3. Hit tiau5 ke-a2-lou7 e5 nng7-peng5 u7 chin che7 keng toa7 keng e5 pah-hoe3-tiam3, gun2 chheng7 tioh8 phoa3-kou5-kou5 e5 che3-hok8 ti7 hia seh8 ke-a2-lou7. KiaN5 kau3 chit8 keng pou3-tiam3 e5 thau5-cheng5 si5, bo5-tiuN-ti5 khi3 khoaN3 tioh8 nng7 saN e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 ti7 lai7-te2 leh boe2 mih8-kiaN7, hit-e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 tioh8 si7 ki5-tiong e5 chit8-e5. Hoat-hian7 tioh8 in e5, tong-jian5 si7 goa2 chit-e5 kau5-gin2-a2. In-ui7, peng5-iu2 sui-jian5 kong2 bo5-ai3 koh cho3 tiat-hak8-ka, tan7-si7 tng5 si5-kan i2-lai5, i u7 po2-chhi5 khoaN3 thou5-kha e5 sip8-koan3. Thoe3 chit8-pou7 kong2, tioh8 sng3 i bo5 khoaN3 thou5-kha e5 sip8-koan3, sui2 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 e5 chu-iong5 ma7 bo5 kho2-leng5 e7 cheng3-khak e5 thang3 koe3 i e5 bak8-kiaN3. Goa2 iong7 chhiu2 pass chit-e5 am3-ho7 hou7 peng5-iu2, in-ui7 gun2 bo5 hoat-tou7 lai5 kong2-oe7, goa2 kiaN kong2-oe7 e7 khi3 hou7 chia e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 hoat-hian7 gun2 leh chu3-i3 in. peng5-iu2 sui5 tioh8 liau2-kai2 goa2 e5 i3-su3, i thau-thau-a2 iong7 se3-siaN-oe7 ka7 goa2 kong2 :¡§ Ki-hoe7 lai5 ah ! ¡¨ 
  Goa2 liau2-kai2 i e5 i3-su3. sou2-i2, gun2 ti7 chit8 chang5 chhiu7-a2-kha khia7 teng7, keng-koe3 gou7 hun-cheng e5 chham-siong5, gun2 koat-teng7 beh chhai2-chhu2 chek-kek8 e5 heng5-tong7. Iu5 goa2 phah thau5-tin7, chin hiau-pai e5 kiaN5 jip8-khi3 pou3-tiam3. Pou3-tiam3 e5 thau5-ke bin7-sek bo5 kai3 ho2 e5 ka7 gun2 gin5 chit8-e7. Goa2 siuN7 kho2-leng5 si7 in-ui7 gun2 si7 chheng7 che3-hok8 e5 tiong-hak8-seng. Si7 an2-choaN2 gun2 e7 khi3 hou7 lang5 khoaN3-bo5-khi2, it-tit8 kau3 taN, goa2 ma7 iah m7 chai si7 siaN2-mih8 li2-iu5. Pou3-tiam3 e5 tiam3-oan5 peng7 bo5 tui3 gun2 kong2 : ¡§Lang5-kheh, lai7-te2 che7. ¡¨ lai5 hoan-geng5 gun2. M7-koh, che bo5 siaN2 tiong7-iau3. Gun2 chi2-put-ko3 si7 kiaN5 jip8-lai5 chit8 keng kan-taN cha-bou2-gin2-a2 e7 jip8 lai5 e5 tiam3 nia5-nia5. Hit saN e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 oat8-thau5 lai5 ka7 gun2 khoaN3. Ki5-tiong chit8 e5, chheng7 chhiN-ang5-sek e5 saN, chha-put-to si7 chap8-peh hoe3 cho2-iu7 e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2, tioh8 si7 tiaN7-tiaN7 ti7 goa2 e5 bang7 tiong chhut-hian7 e5 lu2-chu2-kak. Ti7 goa2 chiaN3-bin7 khoaN3 tioh8 i e5 bin7 e5 hit si5-chun7, goa2 tioh8 chheng-chheng-chho2-chho2 e5 kam2-kak tioh8 chit tiam2. I u7 chin-chiaN3 iu3 e5 io kah chin-chiaN3 sui2 e5 kha. Goa2 e5 jiat8-cheng5 tioh8 ti7 chit-e5 si5-chun7 tat8 kau3 siong7 koan5 e5 te7-pou7. 
  Bo5 loa7 ku2, in tioh8 kiaN5 chhut pou3-tiam3. Gun2 ma7 toe3 in kiaN5 chhut-khi3. Toe3 ti7 li7 in chha-put-to chap8-pou7 e5 au7-piah-bin7. In kiaN5 kau3 to2-ui7, gun2 tioh8 toe3 kau3 to2-ui7. Na2 chhin-chhiuN7 si7 nng7-chiah tiong-sit8 e5 kau2 kang7-khoan2. Ke-a2-lou7 sng3 tioh8 koaN5-thau3-thau3 e5 hong, nng7 peng5 e5 chhiu7-a2 ma7 sui5 hong teh io5-lai5-io5-khi3, chhiu7-hioh8-a2 cheng7-cheng7 e5 ui3 chhiu7-a2 teng2-koan5 lak loh8-lai5. Sui5 tioh8 hong ti7 thiN teng2 poe-bu2, bo5 loa7 ku2 liau2 au7 tioh8 khin-khin-a2 lak ui3 thou5-kha teng2-koan5. Goa2 tiam7-tiam7-a2 teh thiaN goa2 ka-ki7 sim-chong7 kah toa7-chu7-jian5 sou2 hap8-chau3 chhut-lai5 bong5-bong5-biau2-biau2 e5 siaN-im. Che si7 oan5-choan5 siuN7 be7 kau3 e5 chit8 kiaN7 tai7-chi3. Li2 kam2 be7 kam2-kak kong2 che si7 chin ki5-biau7? Lang5 ti7 i siong7 kek-tong7 e5 si5-chun7, phou2-thong oan5-choan5 be7 khi3 kam2-kak tioh8 e5 siaN-im, keng3-jian5 ti7 chit-e5 si5-chun7 pian3-cho3 si7 se3-kan siong7 ui5-it thiaN e7 tioh8 e5 siaN-im, ji5-chhiaN2 koh lai5 kai2-pian3 gun2 e5 un7-mia7. 
  In kiaN5 jip8-khi3 chit8 keng boe7 chap8-chhe-a2 e5 tiam3. He si7 chit8 keng chiok eh8 e5 tiam3, sou2-i2, gun2 tioh8 bih ti7 chit8 chang5 khoaN3 e7 tioh8 in e5 chhiu7-a2-kha tan2. Ti7 keng-koe3 chit8-toaN7 chin tng5 e5 si5-kan liau2-au7, in saN e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 chiah ui3 hit keng tiam3 kiaN5 chhut-lai5, nng7 ki chhiu2 long2 koaN7 kah toa7-pau se3-pau. Siong7 sui2 hit-e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 kiaN5 ti7 leng7-goa7 nng7 lang5 e5 tiong-ng. Kan-taN i ti7 lou7 tiong oat8-thau5 nng7 kai2 lai5 ka7 gun2 khoaN3. In chiam7-chiam7 ui3 chin lau7-jiat8 e5 ke-a2-lou7 oat lai5 kau3 khah phian-phiah e5 lou7. Gun2 nng7 lang5 toe3 ti7 in e5 au7-piah chha-put-to u7 poaN3-tiam2-cheng e5 si5-kan, kiaN5 kau3 lou7 long2 bo5 lang5 leh kiaN5 ah, piN-a2 e5 chhu3 giong7-beh kau3 lou7 boe2 e5 si5, in saN-lang5 e5 heng5-iaN2 soah hiong5-hiong5 siau-sit khi3. Peng5-iu2 chiok siu7-khi3 it-tit8 cham3 kha. Sui-jian5 si7 ti7 chiok te2 e5 si5-kan lai7, tan7-si7, goa2 khak-khak-sit8-sit8 u7 khoaN3 tioh8 ang5-sek e5 saN, koh lai5, tioh8 khoaN3 tioh8 hit-e5 sui2 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 e5 bin7 leh thau-khoaN3 gun2 chit-peng5. Goa2 ka7 peng5-iu2 kong2 goa2 u7 khoaN3 tioh8 i leh thau khoaN3 lan2. Peng5-iu2 si7 giong7-beh khau3 chhut-lai5. I tu2-a2 ho2 ka7 bak8-kiaN3 theh8 loh8-lai5 leh chhit, sou2-i2 goa2 ka7 kong2 liau2, i chheN-chheN-pong7-pong7 beh ka7 bak8-kiaN3 koa3 khi2-lai5, kiat-ko2 koa3 bo5 ho2, bak8-kiaN3 choaN5 lak loh8-lai5. Ho2-ka-chai3, goa2 ti7 khong-tiong ka7 chiap-khi2-lai5. Gun2 kiaN5 lai5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 chhu3 e5 mng5-kha-khau2, in chhu3 lai7 si7 tiam7-tiam7 bo5 siaN, gun2 soah chit8-si5 khia7 ti7 in mng5-kha-khau2 m7-chai beh an2-choaN2 si7 ho2.
