  Gun2 khi3 pong7 tioh8 piah ah. Bo5 loa7 ku2, peng5-iu2 iong7 chin ut-chut e5 siaN hoe5-tap kong2 :¡§ Goan5-lai5 si7 an2-ne ou. ¡¨ jian5-au7, i iong7 chiok se3-siaN tui3 goa2 kong2 :¡§ lan2 ho2 chau2 ah. ¡¨ Goa2 khin-khin-a2 tam3-thau5 piau2-si7 chan3-seng5. Ma7 m7-chai beh kong2 siaN2-mih8 khah ho2. Ma7 m7-chai si7 an2-choaN2, bo5 keng koe3 toa7-nau2, goa2 tui3 in toa7-hiaN kong2 :¡§ Lin2 sio2-moe7 sit8-chai7 si7 chit8 e7 chiok sui2 e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2. ¡¨ 
