  Koh lai5 hoat-seng e5 tai7-chi3 si7 ti7 goa2 tion-hak8 gou7-ni5 si5, iah tioh8 si7 goa2 chap8-poeh hoe3 si5 e5 kou3-su7. Chha-put-to si7 ti7 hioh-joah8 goa2 tng2-khi3 chhu3 nih, pang3-ka2 teh beh kiat-sok cheng5 hoat-seng e5 tai7-chi3. Si5-kan si7 ti7 poeh8-goeh8-hun7 e5 boe2-liu, jit8-thau5 chiam7-chiam7 bo5 hiah iam7, ke-a2-lou7 khai-si2 u7 hong sau3-jip8-lai5. Ui3 si7-bio7 thoan5-lai5 chu7 kou2-cha2 kau3 taN long2 u7 e5 cheng-siaN, che si7 goa2 iu2 su2 i2 lai5, thau5 chit8 kai2 thiaN tioh8. Chu7-jian5 sou2 che3-cho7 chhut-lai5 bi5-biau7 e5 siaN-im, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 ti7 goa2 e5 sim-lai7 oah8 khi2-lai5. Goa2 chha-put-to si7 ai3 koh chun2-pi7 beh khi3 hak8-hau7 siong7-kho3 ah. 
  Tioh8 an2-ne u7 chit8 kang, toa3 ti7 gun2 tau chhu3-piN, chu7 se3-han3 tioh8 kah goa2 sek8-sai7, tau3-tin7 toa7-han3 e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2, u7 chit8-tin7 i e5 peng5-iu2 lai5 in tau chhit-tho5. I ka7 goa2 kai3-siau7 hou7 i e5 peng5-iu2 sek8-sai7. Am3-tng3 chiah8 liau2-au7, goa2 chhoa7 in lai5 gun2 tau chhit-tho5. Gun2 ti7 goa2 e5 chheh-pang5 khai-kang2 lai5 siau-boa5 si5-kan. Goa2 hoat-kak goa2 oan5-oan5-choan5-choan5 hou7 i e5 tong5-oh8 be5 khi3, ji5-chhiaN2 hui-siong5 hui-siong5 e5 kah-i3 i. Sou2-i2, goa2 tui3 i kong2-oe7 e5 thai7-tou7 chiam7-chiam7 u7 put-an e5 piau2-cheng5 chhut-lai5. Goa2 e5 peng5-iu2 ma7 lu2-lai5 lu2 hoat-kak tioh8 goa2 e5 sim-i3, i choaN5 chin bo5 hoaN-hi2 tui3 i e5 peng5-iu2 kong2 i beh tng2-khi3 ah. Sou2-i2, in tioh8 kiaN5 chhut goa2 e5 pang5-keng. Ti7 beh chau2 chin3-cheng5, goa2 e5 peng5-iu2 thiau-kang ti7 i peng5-iu2 bin7 thau5-cheng5 ka7 goa2 khin-khin e5 lam2 tiau5. Che tui3 gun2 lai5 kong2, sit8-chai7 si7 bo5 kong2 sng3 siaN2 bo5 chu7-jian5 e5 toa7 tiau5 tai7-chi3. Tan7-si7, goa2 siuN7 tioh8 toh8 bo5 hoaN-hi2, kui lan7-pha e5 hoe2. 
  In-ui7 chiok siu7-khi3, sou2-i2 keh-tng2-kang, goa2 sou2 kah-i3 e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 beh tng2 khi3 e5 si5-chun7, goa2 choaN5 bo5 khi3 ka7 sang3. Sit8-chai7 si7 u7 kau3 gong7. Hiah-nih-a2 hou7 goa2 gong7-sin5 e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 beh li7-khui, goa2 keng3-jian5 iah koh to2 ti7 bin5-chhng5 teng2. Se3-kan siong7 kam2 iah u7 hiah-nih-a2 gian3-thau5 e5 lang5 leh ? 
  Goa2 sui5 tioh8 hoan2-hoe2 ah, ji5-chhiaN2 hou7 hoan2-hoe2 lai5 cho2-iu7 goa2 kui e5 lang5 e5 sim-cheng5. Tan7-si7, ho2-ka-chai3 goa2 chai-iaN2 hit-e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 toa3 e5 sou2-chai7. Che e7-tang3 sng3 si7 put-heng7 tiong iah e7-tang3 an-ui3 e5 sou2-chai7. 
  Tng2 khi3 hak8-hau7 liau2, keng-koe3 nng7 ko3 goeh8 e5 si5-kan ah. Ti7 chit-toaN7 ki5-kan, goa2 tui3 hit-e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 e5 siau3-liam7 si7 lu2-lai5 lu2-giong5, su-liam7 i e5 sim-cheng5 si7 it-tit8 tu2 ti7 goa2 e5 sim-koaN-thau5. Tioh8 an2-ne ke3-siok8 kau3 chap8-it goeh8 ah. U7 chit8 e5 le2-pai3, goa7-khau2 chhoe tioh8 chhe-liang5 e5 hong, goa2 koat-teng7 bo5-lun7-ju5-ho5 long2 beh chau2 khi3 in tau chhoe7 i. Sou2-i2, goa2 tioh8 che7 hoe2-chhia, chha-put-to keng koe3 chit8-tiam2-cheng e5 si5-kan, lai5 kau3 chit8 e5 leng2-chheng-chheng e5 chng-kha chhia-thau5 loh8 chhia. Ui7 tioh8 beh hou7 goa2 kek-tong7 e5 sim-cheng5 peng5-cheng7 loh8 lai5, goa2 choaN5 chiam7-si5 khia7 ti7 chhia-thau5 e5 chhut-khau2, him-siong2 chng-kha chhan5-hng5 e5 hong-keng2. Ah, chia tioh8 si7 i tiaN7-tiaN7 leh khoaN3 e5 hong-keng2. Chia ma7 si7 i che7 chhia kah loh8 chhia e5 chhia-thau5. Li2 eng3-kai e7-tang3 liau2-kai2, che sit8-chai7 si7 chit8 e5 chin hou7 lang5 boan2-chiok e5 lian5-siong2. Lang5 e5 iok8-bang7 sit8-chai7 si7 chiok se3 e5. Ui7 tioh8 beh tit tioh8 i, goa2 chin-chiaN3 phah-sng3 beh tam3 chit-e5 phian-phiah e5 chng-kha sou2-chai7 koe3 goa2 e5 au7-poaN3-si3-lang5. Ui3 chhia-thau5 kiaN5 chhut-lai5, chin kin2 tioh8 lai5 kau3 in tau ah. Tan7-si7, tian-to3 kau3 liau2-au7 goa2 soah tiu5-tu5 m7 chai si7-m7-si7 ai3 jip8-khi3, siuN7-tioh8 lai5 kau3 hiah-nih-a2 su-bou7 e5 lang5 e5 mng5-kha-khau2, bo5 jip8-khi3 tioh8 tng2-khi3, an2-ne khi3 si2 ho2 ah. Sou2-i2, goa2 the5-chhut iong2-khi3, khi3 long3 in tau e5 toa7-mng5. Chhut lai5 ka7 goa2 khui-mng5 e5 si7 chit8 e5 khoaN3 khi2 lai5 chin ko-kui3, si3-chap8 hoe3 cho2-iu7 e5 cha-bou2-lang5. 
  ¡§ ChhiaN2 mng7 si7 siaN2-mih8 lang5 ? ¡¨ 
  Goa2 ka7 goa2 e5 mia5 po3 hou7 i chai-iaN2, i peng7 bo5 siaN2-mih8 piau2-cheng5 e5 kong2 : ¡§ ChhiaN2 jip8-lai5 che7.¡¨ Goa2 choaN5 toe3 i jip8-khi3, che7 ti7 i e5 tui3-bin7. 
  ¡§Lau2-sit8 kong2, goa2 si7 ui7-tioh8 lin2 cha-bou2-kiaN2 e5 tai7-chi3 lai5 beh pai3-thok li2 e5. ¡¨ 
  ¡§Gun2 cha-bou2-kiaN2 u7 hiong3 goa2 the5 khi2 koe3 li2 e5 tai7-chi3, sou2-i2 li2 m7-bian2 kheh-khi3, u7 siaN2-mih8 tai7-chi3 cho3 li2 kong2. ¡¨ 
  Goa2 su-bou7 e5 lang5 e5 lau7-bu2 i3-goa7 e5 iong7 chiok chhin-chhiat e5 thai7-tou7 kah gian5-gu2 lai5 tui3-thai7 goa2, goa2 siuN7 che it-teng7 si7 in-ui7 goa2 kong2-oe7 thun-thun-thou2-thou2, chiok kin2-tiuN e5 khoan2, i siuN7 beh lai5 an-ui3 goa2 e5 goan5-in. Goa2 goan5-pun2 chun2-pi7 ho2 chiok che7 e5 tai5-su5, cho3 chit8-e7 long2 chau2 kau3 na5-au5 giong7-beh kong2 chhut-lai5. Tan7-si7, goa2 chit8-si5 soah m7 chai beh soan2 to2 chit8-ku3 kong2 khah ho2. Goa2 siuN7 beh kong2 e5 oe7, chit8-e5 chit8-e5 long2 ti7 goa2 e5 siaN-toa3 e7-kha, tan7-si7 bo5 chit8-e5 si7 khah sek-tong3, kong2 chhut-lai5 khah the2-bin7. Tiam3 ti7 chit-khoan2 e5 chong7-hong2 ha7, goa2 si7 u7 kau3 kian3-siau3. Tioh8 ti7 chit-e5 si5-chun7, tut8-jian5 kan goa2 khi3 siuN7 tioh8 chit8-ku3 chiok tho3-tong3 e5 oe7, chit-ku3 oe7 i2 chin beng2 e5 khi3-se3, iaN5 koe3 ki5-thaN sou2-u7 e5 oe7, ui3 goa2 e5 siaN-toa3 poe chhut-lai5.
  ¡§A-m2, chhiaN2 li2 ka7 cha-bou2-kiaN2 ke3 hou7 goa2. ¡¨ 
  Kong2 chhut chit-ku3 oe7 e5 lang5 peng7 m7-si7 goa2, si7 oe7 pun2-sin kho3 I ka-ki7 e5 khi3-se3, ui3 goa2 e5 siaN-toa3 piang3 chhut-lai5 e5. Tan7-si7, put-koan2 ju5-ho5, chit-ku3 oe7 si7 chit8-ku3 chin ho2, chin oan5-bi2 e5 chit8-ku3 oe7. Tong-jian5, I peng7 bo5 hoat-hui tioh8 I eng3-kai u7 e5 hau7-ko2. Tan7-si7, it-tit8 kau3 taN, goa2 ma7 iah si7 jin7-ui5 kong2, che si7 goa2 chit8-si3-lang5 tiong kong2 koe3 siong7 ui2-tai7 e5 chit8-ku3 oe7. 
  A-m2 iong7 chin ke7 e5 siaN-tiau7 lai5 hoe5-tap goa2. 
  ¡§Chin-chiaN3 chiok phaiN2-se3, I ti7 kou3-hiong i2-keng hou7 lang5 koaN7-tiaN7 ah, chin to-sia7 li2 e7-tang3 tui3 gun2 cha-bou2-kiaN2 hiah ho2, m7-koh in-ui7 an2-ne, sou2-i2 bo5 hoat-tou7 lai5 tat8-seng5 tioh8 li2 e5 ng3-bang7, goa2 kam2-kak chin sit-le2. Ji5-chhiaN2, I e5 lau7-pe7 ti7 chit8-le2-pai3 cheng5 koe3-sin, gun2 ti7 choe3-kin7 ma7 tioh8 ai3 tng2-khi3 kou3-hiong ah. ¡¨ 
  A-m2 e5 siaN, kho2-leng5 si7 goa2 chu2-koan e5 jin7-teng7, pian3-cho3 chiok pi-siong e5 khoan2. ThiaN tioh8 in lau7-pe7 koe3-sin e5 siau-sit, goa2 ma7 kiaN chit8-tio5. Goa2 ka7 bak8-chiu khoaN3 ui3 keh-piah e5 pang5-keng khi3, peh8-bong5-bong5 e5 ian ui3 iong7 sin-e5 peh8-sek e5 pou3 kham3 tiau5 e5 kut-thoaN3 koan3-thau5 chiam7-chiam7 phiau khi2-lai5. KhoaN3 tioh8 chit-khoan2 cheng5-heng5, hou7 goa2 tut8-jian5 kan kam2-kak siong-sim khi2-lai5. Goa2 ka7 a-m2 kong2: ¡§Chin sit-le2 a-peh koe3-sin e5 tai7-chi3 goa2 long2 m7 chai-iaN2. Li2 kam2 e7-tang3 hou7 goa2 ka7 a-peh tiam2 chit8-ki-a2 hiuN? ¡¨ 
  Ti7 chit-e5 si5-chun7, ui3 chhan-thiaN e5 choa2-mng5 tiong-kan chhut-hian7 liau2 chit8-e5 chheng7 tiong-hak8 che3-hok8 e5 siau3-lian5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 e5 iaN2. Ah, he m7 tioh8 si7 goa2 chham bin5-bang7 tiong ia7 leh siau3-liam7 e5 heng5-iaN2. I tui3 goa2 bi5-bi5-chhio3 chit8-e7, tan7-si7 sui5 tioh8 koh siau-sit chong-iaN2 bih khi3 au7-piah ah. Kho2-leng5 I kiaN hou7 in lau7-bu2 hoat-hian7. I e5 chhut-hian7 hou7 goa2 e5 sim-chong7 pok8-pok8-thiau3, na2 leh long3-cheng kang7-khoan2. Tan7-si7, in lau7-bu2 i2-keng khia7 khi2-lai5 ah, sou2-i2 goa2 chi2-ho2 toe3 ti7 I e5 au7-piah, kiaN5 jip8-khi3 keh-piah e5 pang5-keng. In lau7-bu2 the3 goa2 tiam2 hiuN liau2, goa2 chin khian5-seng5 ti7 in lau7-pe7 e5 sin5-chu2-pai5-a2 thau5-cheng5 pai3-pai3. Goa2 ka7 thau5-khak taN3 hou7 ke7-ke7 pai3 chiok ku2. Hut-jian5 kan, goa2 kam2-kak tioh8 sio-sio e5 bak8-sai2 ui3 goa2 e5 bin7 nng7-peng5 lau5 loh8-lai5, goa2 kin2 iong7 chhiu2 khi3 ka7 chhit tiau7. M7-si7, goa2 choat8-tui3 bo5 kho2-leng5 e7 khau3 chiah tioh8. Kho2-leng5 goa2 chi2-si7 kam2-kak tioh8 u7 saN2-mih8 chiok tang7 e5 mih8-kiaN7 teh ti7 goa2 e5 heng-kham2 nia7-nia7. Goa2 khia7 khi2-lai5, tng2-khi3 keh-piah e5 pang5-keng theh8 goa2 hit teng2 iong7 chiaN5 ku2, i2-keng teh piN2 e5 bo7-a2.
  ¡§Kiau2-jiau2, goa2 ho2 lai5 ko3-si5 ah, a-m2.¡¨ kong2 liau2, goa2 tioh8 ong2 goa7-khau2 chau2 chhut-khi3. Bo5 tiuN-ti5 e5 chit-e5 tong7-chok hou7 a-m2 kiaN chit8-e7, I jiok ui3 goa2 e5 au7-piah lai5. Tan7-si7 goa2 it-tit8 chau2 kau3 toa7-mng5 khau2, chiah koh oat8-thau5 khoaN3, goa2 khoaN3 tioh8 goa2 sim-ai3 e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2 e5 bin7 ti7 I e5 lau7-bu2 e5 au7-piah chhut-hian7. 
  Goa2 koh toa7-siaN hoah chit8 kai2: ¡§A-m2, chai3-hoe7.¡¨ Tan7-si7, a-m2 kho2-leng5 peng7 bo5 thiaN-tioh8. In-ui7, goa2 siuN7 kho2-leng5 chi2-si7 goa2 ka-ki7 jin7-teng7 kong2 goa2 u7 hoah, ki5-sit8 peng7 bo5 chin-chiaN3 ui3 goa2 e5 chhui3 kong2 chhut-lai5. Sian7-liong5 e5 li2, che tioh8 si7 goa2 e5 loan5-ai3 keng-koe3, kou3-su7 ma7 kau3 chia ui5-chi2, thiaN liau2 kam2-kak an2-choaN2? Ui3 hit-chun7 khai-si2, goa2 tioh8 m7-bat koh khoaN3 koe3 I ah. In-ui7, chha-put-to koh koe3 si3-ko3-goeh8 au7, goa2 tioh8 ui3 tiong-hak8 chhut-giap8 ah, I ma7 kang7-khoan2 ui3 hak8-hau7 chhut-giap8, kah I kang7-pan ma7 si7 goa2 chhu3-piN e5 peng5-iu2, ma7 chhut-giap8 ah. Kau3 si3-goeh8 te2 cho2-iu7, goa2 thiaN chhu3-piN leh kong2, goa2 e5 ai3-jin5 kah I e5 lau7-bu2 tau3-tin7 tng2-khi3 kau3 chin hng7 e5 kou3-hiong ah. Chiong goa2 kah I khan cho3-hoe2 e5 hit-tiau5 soaN3 tioh8 an2-ne tng7 khi3 ah. Si5-kan tauh8-tauh8-a2 leh koe3, goa2 tui3 I e5 su-liam7 ma7 chiam7-chiam7 leh kiam2-chio2, siong7 boe2-a2, ma7 ka7 I pang3 be7 ki3 ah. Koh koe3 nng7-ni5 liau2-au7, thiaN tioh8 I i2-keng kiat-hun e5 siau-sit, tan7-si7 goa2 peng7 bo5 siu7 tioh8 chin toa7 e5 chhi3-khek. Chit-e5 siau-sit si7 ui3 goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 kah toa3 ti7 gun2 tau keh-piah e5 peng5-iu2 kong2-oe7 tiong thiaN lai5 e5. 
  Li2 siuN7 I boe2-a2 e7 pian3-cho3 siaN2 khoan2? Ki5-sit8, chham goa2 ma7 si7 bo5 hoat-tou7 liau2-kai2. M7-koh, au7-lai5 ma7 hoat-seng chit8-kiaN7 chin be7-tang3 hou7 lang5 siong-sin3 e5 tai7-chi3. He si7 hoat-seng ti7 gun2 hun-khui si3-tang au7 e5 bou2 chit8-kang, goa2 siu tioh8 I kia3 lai5 e5 phoe. Phoe e5 teng2-koan5 kan-taN u7 I e5 mia5 nia7-nia7, peng7 bo5 sia2 I e5 chu7-chi2. It-tit8 kau3 chit-ma2 goa2 ma7 iah e7 ki3-tit hit-tiuN phoe e5 lai7-iong5.
  "Hun-chhiu2 liau2-au7, ti7 chui3-bang7 tiong koe3 si3-ni5 ah. Mui2 chit8-kang, goa2 su-liam7 li2 e5 hong-chhai2, hoai5-liam7 li2 e5 phiau-phiat, chhim-chhim khek-in3 ti7 goa2 e5 sim-koaN te2. Bo5 lang5 e7-tang3 lai5 chai-iaN2 goa2 su-bou7 li2 e5 sim-cheng5. Tan7-si7, lan2 nng7-lang5 hun-khui ti7 hiah-nih-a2 hng7 e5 sou2-chai7, m7 chai si7-m7-si7 u7 ki-hoe7 koh lai5 kah li2 saN-kiN3. Chit-ma2 e5 goa2 kan-taN e7-tang3 hoe5-ek tioh8 hit chit8-kang li2 toa3 tioh8 pi-ai kah toan7-chhiang5 e5 sim-cheng5 lai5 li7-khui gun2 tau si5 e5 cheng5-keng2. Goa2 chin-chiaN3 chiok hio7-hoe2, chiok au3-nau2, si7 an2-choaN2 goa2 ti7 hit chit8-kang bo5 lai5 the5-chhut iong2-khi3, chau2 khi3 li2 e5 bin7-thau5-cheng5, hiong3 li2 kong2 chhut goa2 kou-loan5 e5 bu5-nai7? Chit-toaN7 oan3-than3 e5 koe3-khi3, khiong2-kiaN goa2 chit8-si3-lang5 long2 bo5 hoat-tou7 lai5 pang3 be7 ki3-tit. Chu7 goa2 thau5 chit8-kai2 ti7 li2 e5 chheh-pang5 kah li2 sek8-sai7 liau2-au7, goa2 tioh8 thau-thau khi3 ai3 tioh8 li2 ah. Tan7-si7, goa2 it-tit8 bo5 hoat-tou7 lai5 hiong3 li2 piau2-tat8 goa2 tui3 li2 e5 su-bou7. Che oan5-choan5 si7 goa2 ka-ki7 loan2-jiok8 bo5-lat8 sou2 cho7-seng5. In-ui7 put-koan2 ju5-ho5 goa2 chong2-si7 ciht8-e5 cha-bou2-gin2-a2. 
  Chai3-hoe7, chai3-hoe7......, li2 iah chin siau3-lian5, sou2-i2, chhiaN2 li2 chhian-ban7 tioh8 ai3 ka7 goa2 pang3 be7 ki3-tit chiah e7-sai2. Goa2 sia2 siong7 boe2-a2 e5 chit-tiuN phoe hou7 li2, goa2 e5 iong7-i3 tioh8 si7 beh tui3 li2 kong2 chit-tiam2. ChhiaN2 li2 po2-tiong7, chai3-hoe7. " 
  Che tioh8 si7 I sia2 lai5 hou7 goa2 e5 phoe. Goa2 goan5-pun2 i2-keng sio liau2 chhun hu e5 ai3-cheng5 hoe2-thoaN3, u7 chit8-pou7-hun7 chha-chit8-tiam2-a2 tioh8 koh toh8 khi2-lai5. Tan7-si7, it-chhe3 long2 bo5 hoat-seng kang7-khoan2, koh peng5-peng5-cheng7-cheng7 koe3-khi3 ah. 
